{
  "stem": "4513.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The restroom in our area were all black, but if you went down to the service center, you had to go into the black restroom as opposed to the white restroom.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were labeled on the door at the service center.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every time I went down to the service center-- they had dances and all for us-- but they still, even in a black-- black-- in the black area, they had white and black restrooms.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had white and black drinking fountains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was always the fact the black drinking fountains were dirty.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I drank out of the white drinking fountains when I needed to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I didn't realize that they were keeping-- somebody was making a record of my violations, as they called them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- you know, this is me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were supposed to-- we were supposed to get on the back of the bus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The way they-- the way they did that was to come up and start loading up first in our-- our regiments, which were at the tail end.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they'd tell you to move to the rear, because you got on, you've got to move to the rear.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you can only fill up a certain percentage of the bus, and then they moved the buses down to the white regiments and they always end up in the front.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I used to walk down two regiments and get on with the white soldiers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And so somebody evidently reported that also. 'Cause later on, I'll tell you, they-- they-- they knew about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So then the first part of your basic training was learning how to do all those things like marching and firing weapons, and all-- all-- all the Army stuff was in the first part.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
